Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,于此世间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有从善意中衍生的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也有从恶意中蜕变的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修引发的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟该判下怎样的定义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,制裁是世界的必然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,使用这非人类所该拥有的力量之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,无论接受与否 心中都会产生孤独的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,自善意与恶意的夹缝堕落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,若有人能从那里重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那人便已得到了不容质疑的王者之力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:53.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梦中梦见过的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:57.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}远在无尽的天边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:04.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干涸往日的天色 在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:09.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相等间隔 喧嚣中跌倒爬起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:14.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}于此时间间隔皆无的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:18.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等身大小 掀起滔天阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}造出我真实的容颜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完美无缺 即使仅有半面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:29.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始腐烂的苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:33.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掉落到我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:40.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用镜子映出我心灵的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:45.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遥远感觉 人海中跌倒爬起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:50.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}于此时间感觉皆无的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头身大小 伸出锐利爪锋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:57.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}削出我崭新的容颜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:02.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完美无缺 即使仅有半面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:11.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}——遥远感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:17.37,TITLE,,0,0,0,,被囚禁的娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,按照计划进行红莲贰式再调整后的熟悉训练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,京都和印度军区已经谈妥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,之后只等开发小组与拉克夏塔的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,组织的细胞化现为92%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,构成人员也按从1到14的阶层划分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,根据ZERO的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不列颠管辖的仓库里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也已安排了我们的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,关东地区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,将全564处地点的战力和人员分散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,被发现的我方据点有32处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其中虚设据点11处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,被逮捕的有47人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,然而由于与阶层8以上切断了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就连不列颠也无法继续深入调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,加上京都的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,普通民众想要向军队或者警察通报几乎不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不列颠内的协力者名单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就是上次ZERO所安排的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,关于藤堂和四圣剑 仍在搜查中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,继续进行作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗? 由我出任使者…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,妄自菲薄就会被轻视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,中华联邦正是这样的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真没自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你不同 谦虚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就以这种心态去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,护照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,做得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又要被其他家庭收养吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,依然是枢木的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是要去本家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这股怪味是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是垃圾场附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,朱雀 你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,母后告诉过我 人的体温对止泪很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定…要越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好上学是会留级的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也差不了多少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为黑色骑士团的行动越发活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是技术部的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 偶尔也来我家吃个饭如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有预定吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会给你添麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道会长要去相亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今天?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,既然知道为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你的话 你会哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我偏要笑给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 因为我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候别这么纯真地回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,纯真?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样子就是所谓的纯真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那么吃饭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我就去跟娜娜莉说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…上课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只是先告诉她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的烦恼 就被你扔在一边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咲世子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的课不是从第二节开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,吃惊吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟相亲一般都是在酒店或饭店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说洛伊德伯爵是很特别的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别具一格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不错的形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,居然想迎取被剥夺爵位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没落的阿什福德家的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爵位什么的根本无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 只是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那就暂且搁置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 朱雀他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 他叫我不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你大意了呢 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我死了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在C.C.不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟对GEASS无效的对手很棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,若不偿还你之前的大礼 我真是坐立不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该在500米以内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要来找找看?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,时间限制为5小时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 这是我和你的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,若是使用警察这个棋子就要出局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想像上次那样被枪击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过不列颠的医学还真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,托它的福…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那时你下达的GEASS不该是开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而是杀死他才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为你的天真 你妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才会陷入险地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,才会陷入危机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,才会陷入困境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 娜娜莉与此无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,作为游戏 你不认为太过卑劣了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,若你想藉此让哥哥伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你们兄妹俩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.45,NOTE,,0,0,0,,各位 午休了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.40,NOTE,,0,0,0,,有没有在狼吞虎咽?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,夏莉和鲁路修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,会长说要暂时配合他们玩陌生人游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,相亲怎样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,夏莉和鲁路修…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,随他们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是日常的夫妻吵架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这和我毫无关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是那小子想越过那条线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那条线?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧 鲁路修只会纸上谈兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但实战似乎很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,实战…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,经验不足啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,经验…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,午餐不够吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,亚瑟 为什么你总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你对夏莉怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要不送她个礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,比起那个 上课啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,若下午还不去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上的事 等会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在玩赌博吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你倒立着找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我会考虑给你加一个小时哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的焦躁被完全看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为了读取我的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该在500米以内的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 是娜娜莉出了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,饭马上就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,饭?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你出去买东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 材料是现成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还是很害怕外面的不列颠人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有想起什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 什么也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你还受着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,来 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,若能合你口味就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,掳走娜娜莉的是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是…不列颠的皇室?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这和我们的身份没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想把女人占为己有的某个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你被威胁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,若是接受警察调查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的身份也许会被揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 不能向军队或警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只能凭我们来想办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这真的跟赌博…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那 有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只有照片 还有他能够监视我的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 有像水流淌过的声响…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,水?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,循环系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,下面的阶层吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不过真罕见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,若是平时的你 应该会立刻察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,数据被篡改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只好破坏锁定系统了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是违反校规吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下修好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就由我来破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,已经开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是太过娴熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,部份管理是由学生会进行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你从以前到现在 都是用这个逃到外面去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 偶尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,与你推测的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,监视相机连接着机关枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那个系统的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,反应时间大概是0.05秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那就无法从这里出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,先回上面把系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真是乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉在等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 朱雀也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对呢 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,枢木擅自跟来这事我暂且原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,两位就好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会拆除炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我和鲁路修联手没有做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,振子炸弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让运动永不停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,螺线管一直为其提供能量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,若是受到其他外力影响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也要假设移动娜娜莉也会造成爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能预测损害规模吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,半径500米以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,毛在GEASS有效范围外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道解除的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只要切断引爆装置突出的线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是那家伙的专长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,应该能辨别哪些是伪线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 必须要想其他办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能辨别出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要以极微小的动作在钟摆内将线切断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是人类所能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别说得那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,情报太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谨慎自然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个有时间限制吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 情报就在你的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我再怎么说也算个军人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不准备利用这个情报吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,纸巾还有剩余…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,上课真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,总之在毕业前要好好玩个过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是校规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是个笨蛋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,无忧无虑的小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才讨厌学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来他还设了什么陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,毛应该在监视娜娜莉的摄影头信号接收处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到他居然回学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙真是胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫朱雀不要轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我剩下的办法只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 偷腥猫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不带武器也不想策略
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹就这么扔着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有用到黑色骑士团和刚才的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 鲁鲁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不打算对你做解释说明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你有准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 来做个了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的得意项目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,自从来到“11区”后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就尽是发生些预料外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一直做桌面前的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是发胖了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,皇姐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得这个庭院很像吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很像玛丽安娜皇妃的离宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 确实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,听说是克洛维斯皇兄指示的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他出奇的喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,明明总与那里的鲁路修吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有定曾是一对劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对方可更年幼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 在皇兄留下的画里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有画着鲁路修他们的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,得尽快平定这个区域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不然 实在对不起克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,以及鲁路修和娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是兄妹3人生命凋零的土地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个天平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,既是炸弹的引爆装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,亦是解除装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,将要放上的是双方被吃掉的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,当这个指针完全倒向我这边时就爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,倒向你那边时炸弹就会解除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你若获胜 你妹妹就能获救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不良嗜好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪会被C.C.遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,挑衅是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你心里想的我可全都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你并非能让脑袋闲着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你内心总有个自我观察的评论家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还有冷眼注视着这个评论家的另一个自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你想多少花招 我的胜利都不会动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,同时想着7件事来迷惑我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,若将我的GEASS完全锁定在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要看穿哪个是真实的很容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 看来最后的策略也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为你小看我 你妹妹的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,已经毫无办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然想利用他人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可是妹妹娜娜莉被作为人质的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不快点的话…你瞧你瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,时间就不够了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就会失去妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你真要走这一步?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不太清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,放过娜娜莉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是我…是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,终于让我听到你内心深处的声音了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看看四分五裂成什么样子了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是 为了让我集中注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不列颠的准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要以涉嫌扰乱治安拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,朱雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你把炸弹解除了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,居然配合着节拍与速度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为鲁路修已告诉我要切断哪条线了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还说听到叫声就立刻冲进来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,毛 这样就将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我给自己施加GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记了指示过朱雀这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,坚信心声是绝对正确情报的你败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 为了读取我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而缩小效果范围结果导致失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这家伙败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你又准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是如果不相信朱雀便无法成立的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咲世子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,咲世子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为这样就赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放手 你这个弑父的凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在7年前杀死了自己的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为阻止提倡彻底抗战的父亲就能结束战争?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是幼稚!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上你不过就是个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 没被曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了周围的大人全替你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那么说枢木首相以自杀来逃避军务这事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,弥天大谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,若不那么做 日本就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今还是那么嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个罪该万死的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想拯救别人?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是想拯救你自己的内心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想就这么顺水推舟地去死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才总是将自己逼入死地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的善意只是自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是个想要遭受惩罚的小鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾喜欢过你 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你先走一步 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在死后的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:27.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}将一片片马赛克 拼结成美丽画面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:35.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}描绘出你我的相逢 你我的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:49.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}每次都怀着心中的不甘而入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:58.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}醒来之后却依旧徘徊不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:02.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}依旧重复着无谓的徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:11.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}鲜艳的马赛克映出曾经的谎言过错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:18.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}悔恨的心中只想将它们全部抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:26.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}回首望去 最初的起跑线依然还在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:33.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}赶快重拾梦想 重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:41.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}将一片片马赛克 拼结成美丽画面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:48.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}描绘出你我的相逢 你我的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,结果还是没有向毛问出契约的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为何没在再会时…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来 他都想传达给我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那时 我能够和他好好地面对面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:09.46,NEXT,,0,0,0,,骑士
